OL,3,CMan injured in suspected assault while
OL,4,Chouse and three vehicles damaged in
OL,5,Carson
OL,7,FA man has been injured in an incident
OL,8,Fwhich also saw a house and three
OL,9,Fvehicles set alight in Co Antrim.
OL,11,FPolice said substantial damage was
OL,12,Fcaused to the house and vehicles due
OL,13,Fto the fires, and is being
OL,14,Finvestigated as arson with intent.
OL,16,FOfficers received a call to a property
OL,17,Fon the Fairview Lane area of
OL,18,FNewtownabbey around 11pm on Thursday.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/4
