CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F444A1776517870
OL,3,CMan injured in suspected assault while
OL,4,Chouse and three vehicles damaged in
OL,5,Carson
OL,7,F"On officers' arrival, colleagues from
OL,8,Fthe Northern Ireland Fire and Rescue
OL,9,FService were in attendance
OL,10,Fextinguishing the fires which we are
OL,11,Ftreating as arson with intent," police
OL,12,Fsaid.
OL,14,F"The occupants of the property were
OL,15,Fable to evacuate, with a man
OL,16,Fsustaining minor head injuries that we
OL,17,Fbelieve are consistent with a
OL,18,Fsuspected assault.
OL,20,F"Substantial damage was caused to the
OL,21,Fhouse and vehicles due to the fires.
OL,26,@oD@AOUsD@_O]vD@AOU|D@AOU
