OL,3,CMan injured in suspected assault while
OL,4,Chouse and three vehicles damaged in
OL,5,Carson
OL,7,F"We're also investigating the
OL,8,Fpotential that a disturbance and
OL,9,Fassault had occurred inside the
OL,10,Fproperty."
OL,12,FThey added: "Inquiries are continuing
OL,13,Fto determine a motive and who was
OL,14,Finvolved.
OL,16,F"We are keen to hear from anyone who
OL,17,Fmay have CCTV, dash-cam or other
OL,18,Ffootage of the area or who noticed
OL,19,Fsuspicious behaviour.
